{"tid":1301650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[覺得開始有雨革味既入黎]當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調『苦行』，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T23:34:34.000Z","uid":60665,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e3abe9db2746e5877291e69e7d8c74e1f8909e2f","tid":1301650,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"日本社運失敗的歷史<br />\n<br />\n「作者提醒抗爭者，當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調『苦行』，社運人士無論是自己或同路人的要求太高，也不讓人抗爭容下一點輕鬆，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂。如此思考方法，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥，失去了主流社會支持的死胡同。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=86a2b6a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%2F&h=15879f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/日本社運失敗的歷史/</a><br />\n<br />\n話而家抗爭去到依個階段開始失焦似雨革嗰d唔該睇下，一味強調要衝係無用，反而導致失敗<br />\n<br />\n請記得兄弟爬山各有各做先係成功，和理非勇武各有各做，而家政府都自亂陣腳緊，立法會會都開唔到又未有咩大野，你而家又衝又剩咪送頭又無用？所以每星期每區遊行，連儂牆，抵制tvb依d和理非行動係依個時候搞係合適，可以keep著團火去到區選"},{"pid":"d51ebeb256188762d1668ca721a3aa09ac0eadfe","tid":1301650,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99a06c49fc569b78b4f1019077c6bb0b919c4d95","tid":1301650,"uid":33635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n幫手推俾多啲人